{"id":31,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":31,"title":"D&C 27","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 27"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given to Joseph Smith the Prophet, at Harmony, Pennsylvania, August 1830. In preparation for a religious service at which the sacrament of bread and wine was to be administered, Joseph set out to procure wine. He was met by a heavenly messenger and received this revelation, a portion of which was written at the time and the remainder in the September following. Water is now used instead of wine in the sacramental services of the Church."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.1-4"},"1–4"],", The emblems to be used in partaking of the sacrament are set forth;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.5-14"},"5–14"],", Christ and His servants from all dispensations are to partake of the sacrament;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.15-18"},"15–18"],", Put on the whole armor of God."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.1","order":"06.05.027.3221"},["b","1"],"Listen to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"voice"],"of Jesus Christ, your Lord, your God, and your Redeemer, whose word is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"quick"],"and powerful."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.2","order":"06.05.027.3222"},["b","2"],"For, behold, I say unto you, that it mattereth not what ye shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"eat"],"or what ye shall drink when ye partake of the sacrament, if it so be that ye do it with an eye single to my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"glory"],"—",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"remembering"],"unto the Father my",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"body"],"which was laid down for you, and my",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"blood"],"which was shed for the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_2f"},"remission"],"of your sins."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.3","order":"06.05.027.3223"},["b","3"],"Wherefore, a commandment I give unto you, that you shall not purchase",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"wine"],"neither strong drink of your enemies;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.4","order":"06.05.027.3224"},["b","4"],"Wherefore, you shall partake of none except it is made",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"new"],"among you; yea, in this my Father’s kingdom which shall be built up on the earth."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.5","order":"06.05.027.3225"},["b","5"],"Behold, this is wisdom in me; wherefore, marvel not, for the hour cometh that I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"drink"],"of the fruit of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"vine"],"with you on the earth, and with",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"Moroni"],", whom I have sent unto you to reveal the Book of Mormon, containing the fulness of my everlasting gospel, to whom I have committed the keys of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_5d"},"record"],"of the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_5e"},"stick"],"of",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_5f"},"Ephraim"],";"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.6","order":"06.05.027.3226"},["b","6"],"And also with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Elias"],", to whom I have committed the keys of bringing to pass the restoration of all things spoken by the mouth of all the holy prophets since the world began, concerning the last days;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.7","order":"06.05.027.3227"},["b","7"],"And also John the son of Zacharias, which Zacharias he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"(Elias)"],"visited and gave promise that he should have a son, and his name should be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"John"],", and he should be filled with the spirit of Elias;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.8","order":"06.05.027.3228"},["b","8"],"Which John I have sent unto you, my servants, Joseph Smith, Jun., and Oliver Cowdery, to ordain you unto the first",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"priesthood"],"which you have received, that you might be called and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"ordained"],"even as",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"Aaron"],";"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.9","order":"06.05.027.3229"},["b","9"],"And also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Elijah"],", unto whom I have committed the keys of the power of turning the hearts of the fathers to the children, and the hearts of the children to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"fathers"],", that the whole earth may not be smitten with a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"curse"],";"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.10","order":"06.05.027.3230"},["b","10"],"And also with Joseph and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Jacob"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"Isaac"],", and Abraham, your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"fathers"],", by whom the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"promises"],"remain;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.11","order":"06.05.027.3231"},["b","11"],"And also with Michael, or",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Adam"],", the father of all, the prince of all, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"ancient"],"of days;"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.12","order":"06.05.027.3232"},["b","12"],"And also with Peter, and James, and John, whom I have sent unto you, by whom I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"ordained"],"you and confirmed you to be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"apostles"],", and especial",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"witnesses"],"of my",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"name"],", and bear the keys of your ministry and of the same things which I revealed unto them;"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.13","order":"06.05.027.3233"},["b","13"],"Unto whom I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"committed"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"keys"],"of my kingdom, and a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"dispensation"],"of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"gospel"],"for the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_13e"},"last times"],"; and for the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_13f"},"fulness"],"of times, in the which I will gather together in",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_13g"},"one"],"all things, both which are in heaven, and which are on earth;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.14","order":"06.05.027.3234"},["b","14"],"And also with all those whom my Father hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"given"],"me out of the world."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.15","order":"06.05.027.3235"},["b","15"],"Wherefore,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"lift up"],"your hearts and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"rejoice"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"gird"],"up your loins, and take upon you my whole",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"armor"],", that ye may be able to withstand the evil day, having done all, that ye may be able to",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_15e"},"stand"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.16","order":"06.05.027.3236"},["b","16"],"Stand, therefore, having your loins",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"girt"],"about with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"truth"],", having on the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"breastplate"],"of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_16d"},"righteousness"],", and your feet shod with the preparation of the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_16e"},"gospel"],"of",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_16f"},"peace"],", which I have sent mine",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_16g"},"angels"],"to commit unto you;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.17","order":"06.05.027.3237"},["b","17"],"Taking the shield of faith wherewith ye shall be able to quench all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"fiery"],"darts of the wicked;"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.18","order":"06.05.027.3238"},["b","18"],"And take the helmet of salvation, and the sword of my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Spirit"],", which I will pour out upon you, and my word which I reveal unto you, and be agreed as touching all things whatsoever ye ask of me, and be faithful until I come, and ye shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"caught up"],", that where I am ye shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"also"],". Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.1a","order":"06.05.027.3239"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.1b","order":"06.05.027.3241"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/3.29"},"Hel. 3:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.2"},"D&C 6:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.2a","order":"06.05.027.3243"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrament"},"TG Sacrament"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.2b","order":"06.05.027.3245"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/glory"},"TG Glory"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.2c","order":"06.05.027.3247"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-memory"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Memory"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.2d","order":"06.05.027.3249"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrifice"},"TG Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"2e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.2e","order":"06.05.027.3251"},["b","2e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-symbolism-of"},"TG Blood, Symbolism of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2f","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.2f","order":"06.05.027.3253"},["b","2f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/remission-of-sins"},"TG Remission of Sins"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.3a","order":"06.05.027.3255"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/89.5.4-7"},"D&C 89:5 (4–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.4a","order":"06.05.027.3257"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.8"},"Isa. 65:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.5"},"Joel 1:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.18"},"3:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hag/1.11"},"Hag. 1:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/26.29"},"Matt. 26:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.5a","order":"06.05.027.3259"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/14.25"},"Mark 14:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/22.18"},"Luke 22:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.5b","order":"06.05.027.3261"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.14"},"Deut. 32:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.5c","order":"06.05.027.3263"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.16"},"D&C 27:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.20.19-21"},"128:20 (19–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.5d","order":"06.05.027.3265"},["b","5d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-mormon"},"TG Book of Mormon"],"."],["div",{"id":"5e","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.5e","order":"06.05.027.3267"},["b","5e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/37.16"},"Ezek. 37:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"5f","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.5f","order":"06.05.027.3269"},["b","5f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-joseph-people-of"},"TG Israel, Joseph, People of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.6a","order":"06.05.027.3271"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/elias"},"BD Elias"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.7a","order":"06.05.027.3273"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.19.17-19"},"Luke 1:19 (17–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.7b","order":"06.05.027.3275"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.13.13-19"},"Luke 1:13 (13–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.27.27-28"},"D&C 84:27 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.8a","order":"06.05.027.3277"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/13"},"D&C 13"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-aaronic"},"TG Priesthood, Aaronic"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.8b","order":"06.05.027.3279"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/authority"},"TG Authority"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-ordination"},"Priesthood, Ordination"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.8c","order":"06.05.027.3281"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/28.1.1-3,41"},"Ex. 28:1 (1–3, 41)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.13"},"D&C 107:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.9a","order":"06.05.027.3283"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/17.1.1-22"},"1 Kgs. 17:1 (1–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/1.1?span=1.1-2.15"},"2 Kgs. 1:1–2:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/2.2.1-3"},"D&C 2:2 (1–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.38.38-39"},"JS—H 1:38 (38–39)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/genealogy-and-temple-work"},"TG Genealogy and Temple Work"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.9b","order":"06.05.027.3285"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honoring-father-and-mother"},"TG Honoring Father and Mother"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.9c","order":"06.05.027.3287"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-curse-of"},"TG Earth, Curse of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.10a","order":"06.05.027.3289"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/7.25"},"Alma 7:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.10b","order":"06.05.027.3291"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/21.12"},"Gen. 21:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/11.18.17-18"},"Heb. 11:18 (17–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.40"},"1 Ne. 17:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.10c","order":"06.05.027.3293"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/11.9"},"Deut. 11:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.32"},"D&C 98:32"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-origins-of"},"TG Israel, Origins of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.10d","order":"06.05.027.3295"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/32.13.11-13"},"Ex. 32:13 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.11a","order":"06.05.027.3297"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.45.45-48"},"1 Cor. 15:45 (45–48)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.20.19-20"},"2 Ne. 2:20 (19–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.34"},"Moses 1:34"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adam"},"TG Adam"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.11b","order":"06.05.027.3299"},["b","11b"],["a.script